<div class="information">
    <div>Find Local Farmer's Markets/Farms: <br/><a id="link" target="_blank" href="http://www.localharvest.org/cleveland-oh/farmers-markets">LocalHarvest.org</a></div>
    
    <div>What's in season: <br /><a id="link" target="_blank" href="https://ofbf.org/app/uploads/2015/06/whats-in-season.pdf">Produce Chart</a></div>
    
    <div>DIY composting resources:</div>
    <ul>
        <li><a id="link" target="_blank" href="http://eartheasy.com/grow_compost.html">Earth Easy</a></li>
        <li><a id="link" target="_blank" href="https://www.planetnatural.com/composting-101/">Planet Natural</a></li>
    </ul>
    
    <div>NE Ohio Community Gardening Resources</div>
    <ul>
        <li><a id="link" target="_blank" href="http://cccfoodpolicy.org/category/topic/community-gardens">Food Policy Coaltion</a></li>
        <li><a id="link" target="_blank" href="https://cuyahoga.osu.edu/program-areas/agriculture-and-natural-resources/community-gardening">Ohio State University Extension</a></li>
        <li><a id="link" target="_blank" href="http://www.greaterclevelandfoodbank.org/programs/community-gardens">Greater Cleveland Food Bank</a></li>
    </ul>
    
    <div>Useful Books:</div>
    <ul>
        <li><a id="link" target="_blank" href="https://www.amazon.com/Carrots-Love-Tomatoes-Companion-Successful/dp/1580170277">Carrots Love Tomatoes</a></li>
        <li><a id="link" target="_blank" href="https://www.amazon.com/Teaming-Microbes-Organic-Gardeners-Revised/dp/1604691131">Teaming With Microbes</a></li>
    </ul>
</div>
